These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | soul | trance |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | hamster | snake | horse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, train, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | train | taxi | tram |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku, writing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | sudoku | writing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
