.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, martial-arts
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | documentary | martial-arts |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, tea
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate | tea |

