.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | hiking | singing | gardening |

